This weekend at Elephant Park Market, craftsmanship takes centre stage with two incredible makers who pour heart and heritage into everything they create ✨

@pylon_ceramics brings the art of East London to life with wheel-thrown ceramics that are as functional as they are beautiful. Each piece shaped by hand, grounded in intention, and made to be lived with and loved for years to come 🏺

Alongside them, @annmarieeamleia is showcasing her stunning collection of bespoke handmade fashion from flowing kimonos to bold capes, scarves, and bags, each design is a celebration of individuality, style, and skilled artistry 🧵👘

Taking photos for tonight's shop update and dreaming of getting dressed up to go out again. 
@jadegallupstudio porcelain ring and @natalie_lea_owen earrings at the ready!
